summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Insurance CRM system. All core functionality working correctly including login, navigation, upload processing, data review, and field mapping. Successfully verified Foremost Signature file processing with 423 extracted records and proper conflict detection.

flaky_endpoints.symptoms: Agent creation fails due to duplicate agent code
flaky_endpoints.workaround: Use unique agent codes for testing

integration_issues.issue: Difficulty accessing carrier detail page from carriers list

passed_tests: User login flow with test@example.com / test123 credentials
Navigation between Dashboard, Carriers, Upload Center, and Data Review pages
Upload Center page loads with carrier selection dropdown
Foremost Signature carrier exists and is selectable for uploads
Data Review page displays 423 extracted records from Foremost upload
Record filtering by status (conflict filter shows 422 records)
Record detail view shows mapped fields and conflicts
Field mappings applied correctly (EFFECTIVE_DATE, AGENT_CODE, BROKER_ID, etc.)
Conflict detection working (2098 conflicts detected with detailed mismatch info)
Sidebar navigation between all major pages
Upload dropzone functionality and file type validation
Recent uploads display with status and record counts
